Izzat Ibrahim al-Douri died in fighting with government troops in Salahuddin province . 
  He was an Iraqi military commander and deputy to Saddam Hussein until 2003 US-led invasion of Iraq . 
  He headed the Naqshbandi Order insurgent group behind the rise of ISIS . 
  Was the King of Clubs in the pack of cards the US issued of wanted members of Saddam's regime . 
 